OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFog patches will clear this
OL,6,Fmorning to leave a dry start for many
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunny spells, turning
OL,8,Fhazy at times. Clouding over in the
OL,9,Fnorth and west with some outbreaks of
OL,10,Fpatchy light rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA band of cloud continues to
OL,13,Fmove southeast, perhaps with the odd
OL,14,Fspot of rain at times. Fog patches are
OL,15,Fpossible in the south and a patchy
OL,16,Frural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
