OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FDry for many with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine. Thicker cloud and outbreaks
OL,7,Fof heavy rain will move into northern
OL,8,FScotland later with strong winds. Cool
OL,9,Fin the north, warmer in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
